              "items": [
                {
                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3sx64w6x/manifest/annotation/p4",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>I was in hopes he would have<lb/> been thankful for our consideration<lb/> in giving\n                him what he did not deserve<lb/> but he has thought it wiser to seek<lb/> justice in\n                a court of Law</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I shall be obliged by your favour<lb/>-ing me with his precedents,\n                &amp; all<lb/> you know about him prior to his<lb/> coming here, why he was\n                dismissed<lb/> from the congregations as well<lb/> as from the school which he\n                super<lb/>=intended. It is necessary for the Vin<lb/>-dication of the cause of\n                Virtue &amp; jus<lb/>=tice we have Black sheep around<lb/> us &amp; no one should be\n                allowed<lb/> to wear a cloak who is unworthy<lb/> of it &amp; if this man is a\n                drunkard<lb/> why the better for us &amp; all <placeName>Israel</placeName>\n                that<lb/> the mark should be torn from<lb/> his face. We have been favored<lb/> with\n                the presence of the <persName>Rev H. Jacobs</persName><lb/> of\n                    <placeName>Richmond</placeName> who preached last <date>Sabbath</date><lb/>\n                &amp; will do so on the next, his hearers<lb/> were much pleased with his mild<lb/>\n                &amp; gentlemanly manner &amp; his discourse<lb/> was plain &amp; sensible. He is no\n                orator<lb/> our people are much pleased with his<lb/> manners &amp; he is\n                intelligent &amp; no doubt a<lb/> good &amp; con<add>?</add> Jew. As ever your\n                friend</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(7)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">Samuel Hart Sen</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3sx64w6x/canvas/p4"
                }
